title: Gitshock Dex
text: Gitshock Swap is a multinetwork decentralized exchange (DEX) aggregator powered by GTFX token. We allow users to swap, create tokens, stake and create pool easier!

title: Kangaroo Wallets
text: Kangaroo brings payments infrastructure and fiat on/off ramp solutions to users, wallets and apps in the Gitshock Ecosystems.

title: Sitesia
text: One Of Utility Gitshock Finance, Sitesia is a platform that allows you to create your own website in a few minutes. You can create a website for your business, your blog, your portfolio, your online store, etc.

title: Gitshock Enterprise
text: Gitshock Enterprise is a platform building blockchain for business. We provide a suite of products and services to help businesses build, launch, and manage their own blockchain networks.

title: Neware Chain
text: Neware Chain is a blockchain based on Cosmos SDK, which is a blockchain framework that allows developers to build their own blockchain networks.

title: Gitshock Bridge
text: Gitshock Bridge is a cross-chain bridge that allows users to transfer assets between different blockchains.

title: CCTIP Wallet
text: Securely Hold, Send, Receive, Exchange, Tip and Earn 800+ cryptocurrencies with Cwallet.

title: Forbole Big Dipper
text: Big Dipper is an open-source block explorer for a growing list of Interchain blockchains. Our aim is to build a modular and customizable explorer that can support any blockchain.

title: Gitshock Faucet
text: Gitshock Faucet is a platform that allows you to get free Gitshock tokens.

title: Blockscout
text: Blockscout provides a comprehensive, easy-to-use interface for users to view, confirm, and inspect transactions on EVM (Ethereum Virtual Machine) blockchains.

title: Gitshock Explorer
text: Gitshock Scan is a tool for inspecting and analyzing EVM based blockchains. Blockchain explorer for Gitshock Networks.

title: Gitshock DAO
text: Gitshock DAO is a community driven governance which aim to support the mission of Gitshock Finance, to provide a suitable network where everyone, including enterprise and SMEs can adopt crypto easier than before. Gitshock DAO will be by Gitshock Labs and aim to involve various global web3 societies
